value.0: The Mage Guard are a small but well-trained force of growing number within the Kingdom of Kohlingen. The symbol of Mystra emblazoned on their cloaks, they work diligently alongside the Silver Dragons under the command of the Magister.
Set into a copper band is a single green eye, constantly scanning the area and blinking now and then.  When the eye spots something, a faint tingle can be felt in the ring finger.

He whom here lies enclosed in stone,
Was Gregory Simmons, first of his name.
He was Protector of his country, a warrior of red,
Ever the bastion, never one for fame.
Chosen by his people to lead a fraught land,
Justicar for one summer, king for another.
Fighting bravely in war, he led with compassion,
He looked upon all as sister and brother.
He succumbed to the Blade but suffered with grace,
Placing his people first in every manner.
Beloved by Queen and Son, by kin and subject,
His memory and his love live on under his banner.
